nt\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CurrencyService response average duration increased significantly.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这种分析可以帮助你确定系统性能瓶颈所在，并制定进一步的追踪和优化计划。", "metric_analysis_findings": "从收集到的数据中分析，以下是显著的异常指标及相关实体：\n\n### 发现的异常指标及实体\n1. **Node 异常:**\n   - **指标:** `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`\n     - **Node:** `aiops-k8s-08` 显著增加 (正常值: 6515527680.0, 故障值: 10008182784.0)\n   - **指标:** `node_cpu_usage_rate`\n     - **Node:** `aiops-k8s-08` 增加 (正常值: 33.42, 故障值: 49.08)\n\n2. **Service 性能异常:**\n   - **指标:** `rrt_max`\n     - **Service:** `emailservice` (Pod: `emailservice-2`) 显著增加 (正常值: 10296.72, 故障值: 61541.8)\n     - **Service:** `paymentservice` (Pod: `paymentservice-0`) 显著增加 (正常值: 4714.24, 故障值: 25643.8)\n   - **指标:** `rrt`\n     - **Service:** `currencyservice` (Pod: `currencyservice-0`) 值上升 (正常值: 1294.04, 故障值: 1282.47)\n     - **Service:** `shippingservice` (Pod: `shippingservice-1`) 值下降但波动 (正常值: 2144.54, 故障值: 1253.34)\n\n### 归因分析与假设\n1. **Node级故障 (aiops-k8s-08):**\n   - **根因:** `aiops-k8s-08`\n   - **原因:** Node内存和CPU使用率显著提升，影响相关Pod运行。\n   - **证据:** `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`, `node_cpu_usage_rate` 的显著变化。\n\n2. **Pod级故障 (emailservice-2):**\n   - **根因:** `emailservice-2`\n   - **原因:** `rrt_max` 显著增加，影响邮件服务响应时间。\n   - **证据:** `rrt_max` 的异常波动在故障期间显著增加。\n\n3. **Pod级故障 (paymentservice-0):**\n   - **根因:** `paymentservice-0`\n   - **原因:** 支付服务的 `rrt_max` 显著增加。\n   - **证据:** `rrt_max` 的异常变化。\n\n### JSON输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"memory_usage\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node内存和CPU使用率显著提高，影响相关Pod。相关指标有: node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes, node_cpu_usage_rate。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Node aiops-k8s-08的node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从6515527680.0显著提升到10008182784.0, node_cpu_usage_rate从33.42提升到49.08。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"邮件服务的rrt_max显著增加，影响响应时间，相关指标有: rrt_max。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"emailservice-2中的rrt_max从正常的10296.72上升到故障时的61541.8。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"支付服务的rrt_max显著增加，相关指标有: rrt_max。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-0中的rrt_max从4714.24上升到故障时的25643.8。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
